Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_drive(25.10)                                          reset_drive(25.10)

Name
       reset_drive

Syntax
         reset_drive <port_list>

       Resets  the drive previously asserted with the set_drive command on in-
       put  ports.  The  reset_drive  command  removes  assertions   for   all
       rise/fall, minimum/maximum combinations for which the assertion exists.

Parameters
       <port_list>
              Specifies  a  list of input or bidirectional ports for which the
              drive resistance is reset.

Related Information
              * set_drive

